data.description: Rare find for the area.  This home was built in 2009. Open spacious ranch home with amazing kitchen Lots of cabinets and counter space for all those family get togethers. Ceramic flooring in kitchen and bathrooms, Quality laminate flooring throughout. Master has it all, walk in ceramic shower and soak tub double sink and walk in closet. Living room is 26X15  and kitchen is 23X15.  Fenced yard, garage and spacious laundry room area off garage.
